---
import data from "../data/dark-fantasy-data.json";
const { nodes, request_examples, response_examples } = data.architecture;
---
<div class="arch-section">
  <div class="security-banner">
    <span class="shield-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</span>
    <span class="security-quote">"The client requests. The server decides."</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="diagram-container">
    {nodes.map((node, index) => (
      <>
        <div class="diagram-node card">
          <div class="node-num">{index + 1}</div>
          <h3>{node.label}</h3>
          <p class="node-summary">{node.summary}</p>
          <div class="node-caption">
            {index === 0 && "The client makes the game feel immediate, but never declares valuable outcomes."}
            {index === 1 && "Typed gameplay messages connect the visual client to the authoritative simulation."}
            {index === 2 && "The server owns the world and validates every action that changes valuable state."}
            {index === 3 && "Durable progress survives reconnects, crashes, and server restarts."}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        {index < 3 && (
          <div class="diagram-connector">
            <span class="arrow-visual" aria-hidden="true">➔</span>
            {index === 0 && (
              <div class="flow-labels">
                <span class="flow-title">Requests</span>
                <ul class="flow-list">
                  {request_examples.slice(0, 4).map(ex => <li>{ex}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            )}
            {index === 1 && (
              <div class="flow-labels">
                <span class="flow-title">Snapshots</span>
                <ul class="flow-list">
                  {response_examples.slice(0, 4).map(ex => <li>{ex}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            )}
            {index === 2 && (
              <div class="flow-labels">
                <span class="flow-title">Persist</span>
                <span class="flow-sub">SQL Trans</span>
              </div>
            )}
          </div>
        )}
      </>
    ))}
  </div>
  
  <div class="linear-text-equivalent sr-only">
    <h4>System Architecture Text Equivalent</h4>
    <p>The system runs in a four-stage authoritative pipeline:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Godot 4.7 Client:</strong> Handles input, rendering, and prediction. It makes requests but does not calculate outcomes.</li>
      <li><strong>WebSocket &amp; Protobuf Protocol:</strong> Sends client requests (Move, Ability, Item Actions) and receives server snapshots (Combat Results, Spawns, Reconciliation).</li>
      <li><strong>Authoritative Go Server:</strong> Owns and validates combat, movement legality, loot, and progression.</li>
      <li><strong>Postgres:</strong> Durably persists account and character progression data.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .arch-section {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .security-banner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.85rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .security-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #ef4444;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .diagram-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .diagram-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 120px 1.2fr 120px 1.2fr 120px 1.2fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  .diagram-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  }

  .node-num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 1.6rem;
    height: 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .diagram-node h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .node-summary {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .node-caption {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    padding-top: 0.65rem;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .diagram-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .arrow-visual {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .arrow-visual {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
  }

  .flow-labels {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .flow-title {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .flow-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .flow-sub {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0,0,0,0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }
</style>
